    {
      "type": "section",
      "title": "🚫 Negative Words = Positive Tag",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "જો વાક્યમાં નીચેના <b>નકારાત્મક શબ્દો</b> આવેલા હોય તો તે <b>નકાર અર્થ</b> સૂચવે છે. તેથી Question Tag <b>હકારમાં</b> આવે."
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "content": {
            "title": "🔴 Negative Words",
            "headers": ["Words", "Example", "Tag"],
            "rows": [
              ["<b>few, little, neither, seldom, none</b>", "Few people know the answer,", "<b>do they?</b>"],
              ["<b>no, hardly, scarcely, rarely, nothing</b>", "He hardly ever comes late,", "<b>does he?</b>"],
              ["<b>never, no one, nobody</b>", "The child never cries,", "<b>does he?</b>"]
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "content": "<b>યાદ રાખો:</b> few = little = નકાર; <b>a few</b> = <b>a little</b> = હકાર<br>• <b>A few</b> friends are waiting outside, <b>aren't they?</b> ✅<br>• <b>Few</b> people know the answer, <b>do they?</b> ✅"
        }
      ]
    },
