      "type": "section",
      "title": "📝 Summary (સારાંશ)",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "list",
          "content": [
            "<b>Basic Rule:</b> Positive → Negative Tag; Negative → Positive Tag",
            "<b>I am:</b> aren't I? (not amn't I)",
            "<b>Let's:</b> shall we?",
            "<b>Imperative:</b> will you? / can't you? (ગુસ્સામાં)",
            "<b>There is/are:</b> isn't/aren't there?",
            "<b>Everyone/Somebody:</b> they વપરાય",
            "<b>Something/Nothing:</b> it વપરાય",
            "<b>Negative words (few, little, never, hardly):</b> Positive Tag",
            "<b>One of the:</b> he/she/it; All of us: we"
